1) multer  :- for image upload 
2) body-parser :- for decrypting req body
3) cors :- to enable cross platform request
4) dotenv :- to manage environment variables
5) mongoose :- client to connect mongodb to node
6) express :- for building api's with express extension
7) bcryptjs :- For encrypting the password
8) nodemon :- for development to watch changes in the server and build code automatically
9) jsonwebtoken :- for authentication token creation
9) Nodemailer:- for email (npm install nodemailer)
                    reference:- https://medium.com/coox-tech/send-mail-using-node-js-express-js-with-nodemailer-93f4d62c83ee